ws.rocket.path.builder

Interface TreeNodeCallback


  • public interface TreeNodeCallback
    Callback contract for TreeNodeBuilder to control key and value object initialization of tree nodes. This callback has power to modify or even replace the objects, so use carefully!

    To apply the callback, it must be provided to the TreeNodeBuilder constructor and it will be used when building the nodes through-out the (sub)tree. However, the callback won't be applied when the builder is given an already created TreeNode.
